text: Joseph Maffioli (18 February 1904 - 10 July 1965) was a French ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1965 deaths Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:People from Chamonix
